===Glyph origin===
{{Han etyl}}
{{liushu|p}} – the Sun. A dot or line was added in the centre to distinguish it from visually similar characters, e.g. {{l|zh|囗}} (early form of {{l|zh|丁}}). Compare earlier forms of the character with the astronomical and astrological symbol for the Sun ([[☉]]) and the Egyptian hieroglyph {{m|egy|𓇳}}.

